window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The classic World War II thriller from the acclaimed master of action and suspense. </p> <p>One winter night, seven men and a woman are parachuted onto a mountainside in wartime Germany. Their objective: an apparently inaccessible castle, headquarters of the Gestapo. Their mission: to rescue a crashed American general before the Nazi interrogators can force him to reveal secret D-day plans. </p>"; 
